{"tag":"tag", "type":"type", "category":"Thinking_RectangleCenter", "size":"349 40", "key":169, "location":"7750 -640", "label":"MDDTools Main Targets"},
{"tag":"tag", "type":"type", "category":"Thinking_PointRightLeft", "size":"691 167", "key":171, "location":"8040 -500", "label":"- Push usability, intuitivness and simplicity in MDD tools\n- Provide a tool with zero-installation\n- Provide a tool that can be used in any OS/Device (as well as mobile platforms)\n- Have an interface with \"nearly\" zero-menu/buttons (paper feeling)\n- Leave most of the space to the drawing canvas\n- Everything is a graph (projects, project structures, files, directories, models, metamodels, code generation, ...)"},
{"tag":"tag", "type":"type", "category":"Thinking_PointRightLeft", "size":"691 167", "key":174, "location":"8040 -210", "label":"- When loading MDDTools you start with a first graph, your workbanch\n- Here projects are nodes with names. Sub-projects or project-modules can be organized via groups or sub-graphs\n- Files are nodes containing text (soon other content will be supported, pictures, html, videos, ...)"},
{"tag":"tag", "type":"type", "category":"Thinking_RectangleCenter", "size":"349 40", "key":175, "location":"7750 -350", "label":"Project Organization"},
{"tag":"tag", "type":"type", "category":"Thinking_PointRightLeft", "size":"691 167", "key":178, "location":"8050 80", "label":"- Target: strive for intuitiveness and minimalistic design\n- Towards zero-buttons, zero-menus, zero-dialogs tool\n- Towards 'all is visible' (avoid hiding information in GUIs)\n- Integration of visual and textual representation (e.g. graph+source code editor)\n- Nearly all should be done by mouse (touch on mobile devices)"},
{"tag":"tag", "type":"type", "category":"Thinking_RectangleCenter", "size":"349 40", "key":179, "location":"7760 -60", "label":"Usability"},
{"tag":"tag", "type":"type", "category":"Thinking_PointRightLeft", "size":"691 167", "key":182, "location":"8060 380", "label":"- Target: easy extension via HTML/JavaScript plugins\n- Projects and models are simply stored into file-system directory structure (no db or custom format) --> easy backup, revision system, manipulation, ..."},
{"tag":"tag", "type":"type", "category":"Thinking_RectangleCenter", "size":"349 40", "key":183, "location":"7770 240", "label":"Customizability"},
{"tag":"tag", "type":"type", "category":"Thinking_PointRightLeft", "size":"691 167", "key":186, "location":"8050 690", "label":"- Currently MDDTools is composed of 4 parts"},
{"tag":"tag", "type":"type", "category":"Thinking_RectangleCenter", "size":"349 40", "key":187, "location":"7760 550", "label":"Modeling Phases"},
{"tag":"tag", "type":"type", "category":"Thinking_RoundedRectangleLeft", "size":"610 157", "key":189, "location":"9170 10", "label":"- Target: graphical creation of DSL\n- Smooth migration from rough to detailed model\n- Meta-model evolves gradually with application model\n- Incremental insertion of properties (visual or structural) in meta-models"},
{"tag":"tag", "type":"type", "category":"Thinking_HexagoneCenter", "size":"150 40", "key":196, "location":"9050 -120", "label":"DSL"},
{"tag":"tag", "type":"type", "category":"Thinking_HexagoneCenter", "size":"150 40", "key":199, "location":"9050 140", "label":"MDD"},
{"tag":"tag", "type":"type", "category":"Thinking_RoundedRectangleLeft", "size":"610 157", "key":200, "location":"9170 270", "label":"- Easy creation of any hierarchical model\n- Support small to large-scale models\n- Allow creation of flat graps (support avoiding sub-graphs, so to make as much as possible models visible in one view)"},
{"tag":"tag", "type":"type", "category":"Thinking_RoundedRectangleLeft", "size":"610 157", "key":203, "location":"9180 540", "label":"- Target: visual creation of code generation process\n- Templates are always runnable program in the target language\n- Easy creation of any template and program\n- Focus on annotations that do not destrory templates\n- Allow substitution, pattern generation or user castom code manipulation"},
{"tag":"tag", "type":"type", "category":"Thinking_HexagoneCenter", "size":"150 40", "key":204, "location":"9060 410", "label":"CG"},
{"tag":"tag", "type":"type", "category":"Thinking_RoundedRectangleLeft", "size":"610 157", "key":207, "location":"9180 810", "label":"- Easy support for animations for any model\n- REST and JavaScript interface"},
